{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Summary</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>The Corpsmen</i> is a deck-building roguelite where you build and lead a team of creatures to fight, hunt and harvest other monsters. Your creatures will grow and learn new skills according to how you construct them. Harvest and collect parts to create new creations and explore the abilities of the creatures you create. In The Corpsmen, you are encouraged to develop your creations and see how they perform, mission after mission. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The City of Somerley. The last bastion of mankind. Protected by its walls and its Corpsmen. You are a Corpsmen; charged with assembling together creatures from the very monsters you fight against. They will grow as you fight for the city. They may fall, but your city will not. You will make them better, faster and stronger than those before.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Create your creatures</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stitch together creatures you have harvested. Tailor them to how you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571960/extras/TCM_card.gif?t=1729670836\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Fight with them</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your creations to brave the frontiers and see the world. Harvest new samples to take back to make new creations. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571960/extras/TCM_Battle.gif?t=1729670836\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>See their Skills Grow</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Grow your creations. Watch as they develop new skills and improve old ones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571960/extras/TCM_UPG.gif?t=1729670836\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Level Up, Buttercup!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1571960/1c75d292b09bbac11b309cad10f75a3ad269dc69.jpg"},{"name":"Milk Run Done","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1571960/4c77b1eadd5b156ef45aa8f802355d0922ea59e4.jpg"},{"name":"Novice No More","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1571960/dc27136b132eb8f1c12de9b0f180c7adc2541da1.jpg"},{"name":"Against All Odds","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1571960/10152fa2cd074424e57dd5a3304600356903af27.jpg"},{"name":"Rookie Numbers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1571960/f90c74af5d6c881579a3bad702b6e4066c8bd7ac.jpg"},{"name":"Combat Veteran","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1571960/7609a942a7f1286dcded82894d93fe894ad7b466.jpg"},{"name":"Combat Specialist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1571960/014799d380488b6a57c6fdd60a1c04c40146572b.jpg"},{"name":"Timber!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1571960/de5ede01de700bdda8117a7e96bad66b80fbbf24.jpg"},{"name":"A Brisk Hike","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1571960/f60bafc55880659b4dceec4c2bc7275e79eebe38.jpg"},{"name":"A Muddy Afternoon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1571960/e61fde7035960fec0248d35d50457d153da39ae2.jpg"}],"total":74},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571960/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729670836","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571960/page.bg.jpg?t=1729670836","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/stor